      <title>PGIM 坚持看跌美国国债，押注美联储仍可能加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/pgim-sticks-with-bearish-treasury-call-on-bet-fed-may-still-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管债券交易员重新押注美联储将降息，但 PGIM 固定收益表示，央行实际上可能倾向于加息。]]></description>
