    <item>
      <title>通胀率接近 2% 之际欧洲央行行长 Centeno 呼吁谨慎调整利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ecb-s-centeno-urges-prudence-on-rates-as-inflation-nears-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员马里奥·森特诺表示，欧洲央行必须审慎地将利率降至既不会刺激经济也不会抑制经济的水平，这表明官员们将需要一段时间才能再次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ecb-s-centeno-urges-prudence-on-rates-as-inflation-nears-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:59:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：对法国局势的担忧加剧欧洲股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对法国政治动荡的担忧加剧，欧洲股市本周创下 10 月以来表现最差的一周。由于交易员寻求避险，美国股指期货下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
